*[[Veeran]]
*[[Adoor Bhasi]]
*[[KPAC Lalitha]]
*[[Sreelatha Namboothiri|Sreelatha]]

==Soundtrack==
The music was composed by [[MG Radhakrishnan]] and lyrics was written by [[Kavalam Narayana Panicker]].

